a development tool that will
allow you to perfect your book

00:05:43.870 --> 00:05:46.060
and streamline your workflow.

00:05:46.100 --> 00:05:50.090
By the end of this session,
you are going to be ready to make some

00:05:50.170 --> 00:05:52.820
of the best books in the iBookstore.

