deciding whether or not to buy your book.

00:16:18.170 --> 00:16:21.000
And that means you want that
sample to be really good,

00:16:21.000 --> 00:16:21.580
right?

00:16:21.820 --> 00:16:27.600
So to do that,
you need to provide a thorough landmarks.

00:16:27.810 --> 00:16:32.370
