00:16:43.530 --> 00:16:45.610
And again,
landmarks uses the nav element.

00:16:45.810 --> 00:16:49.850
So we have added the EPUB type
landmarks to our nav,

00:16:50.070 --> 00:16:56.490
but now we're also using EPUB type
attributes in each of our list items.

00:16:56.850 --> 00:17:01.200
This way, no matter what you've named
your XHTML document as,

00:17:01.360 --> 00:17:08.010
you have a set value or a set tag for
what that content document's job is.

00:17:08.180 --> 00:17:12.340
So for our first example,
we have coverpg.xhtml.

00:17:12.340 --> 00:17:15.090
It has an EPUB type of cover,
